<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/245586-is-it-normal-to-be-totally-confused-about">Is it normal to be totally confused about what&#39;s going on? Because I am.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_245586'><a id="like_count_community_question_245586" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/245586?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">198 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F6088007-neuromancer">like</a></span>

